### ServiceManager requirements
- Borrow(name string) (Service, error) — increment ref count, auto-start if 0→1
- Return(name string)                  — decrement ref count, auto-stop if 1→0
- Register(svc Service)
- Shutdown()                           — stop all services in reverse registration order
- VideoQueue exception: do NOT auto-stop when ref drops to 0 if VideoQueue.video_enabled=true

### BaseWorker embed
- Tap/Notify: fan-out to all registered handlers (goroutine-safe)
- Tap returns unsubscribe func (calling it removes handler)
- Restart: stop + 1s holdoff + start
- WorkerRun receives context.Context, exits on ctx.Done()
- ServiceRestartSignal: sentinel error type, triggers clean restart without logging as error

### Critical
- All goroutines must respect context.Context for clean shutdown
- No panics on production paths
- sync.Mutex everywhere state is mutated
